[SN]TITLE[SN]
Victim confronts rogue lettings agent

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A victim of rogue lettings agent Martin Marcus confronted him after he failed to return her deposit.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
8 July 2016 Last updated at 22:24 BST
These are some excerpts of the recorded conversation when Marcus promises the victim, Hannah Casey, that the money will be returned.
She never received the money, and Marcus, 52, of Ashfield Avenue in Bushey, was subsequently jailed for four and a half years after admitting fraud.
